    "headline": "Costco Results Will Be This Earning Season’s Last Look at the Consumer",
    "summary": "Costco  Wholesale is the last major retailer to report results this earnings season.  After multiple retailers noted, however cautiously, that consumers are still spending, investors will be looking to see if Costco does the same.  For its fiscal third quarter, Costco is expected to earn $4.98 a share, a 16.3% increase from the year-ago period, on a 10% rise in revenue to $69.68 billion.",
